{"id":"ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC","title":"VDM Basic (Interface) View — the foundation layer","phase":6,"phaseName":"Virtual Data Model (VDM)","category":"Virtual Data Model (VDM)","subcategory":"VDM Layers","language":"abap","description":"VDM Basic (Interface) View — the foundation layer","sections":[{"title":"Concept Diagram","description":"<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">VDM (Virtual Data Model) Layer Architecture</text>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 4: Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"75\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Consumption View (Layer 4)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">C_* or R_* prefix · Fiori UI / OData · @UI.* / @Search / @Consumption.* annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- Arrow -->\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"125\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"520\" y=\"142\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">consumes</text>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 3: Composite -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"155\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"178\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Composite View (Layer 3)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"195\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">C_* prefix · Joins multiple Basic views · Business logic, aggregations, currency conversion</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"210\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: C_Travel_Agency — joins Travel + Agency + Booking</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"245\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 2: Basic / Interface -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"250\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"273\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">Basic / Interface View (Layer 2)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"290\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">I_* prefix · Reusable data foundation · Field selection, aliases, simple filters</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"305\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: I_Travel / I_Booking — clean projection of DDIC tables</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"315\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 1: Private -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"345\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"368\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Private View (Layer 1)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"385\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">P_* prefix or no prefix · Internal abstraction · Complex joins, data enrichment, no UI annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: P_Travel_Aggregate — aggregation logic hidden from consumers</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"410\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"435\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- DB Source -->\n  <rect x=\"300\" y=\"440\" width=\"400\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"463\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">HANA DB / DDIC Tables</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"476\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">/DMO/I_Travel_D / /DMO/I_Booking_D / /DMO/I_Agency / ...</text>\n\n  <!-- Right side: Naming conventions table -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"500\" width=\"900\" height=\"235\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"523\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">VDM Naming Convention & Layer Purpose</text>\n  <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"530\" x2=\"930\" y2=\"530\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <!-- Table header -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"538\" width=\"860\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Prefix</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Purpose</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Consumed By</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"560\" x2=\"930\" y2=\"560\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <!-- Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"560\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">C_* / R_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Consumption</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fiori UI, OData exposure</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@UI.*, @Search, @Consumption.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fiori App / External API</text>\n\n  <!-- Composite -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"600\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">C_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Composite</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Business logic, joins, aggregations</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@ObjectModel.*, @Analytics.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Consumption views</text>\n\n  <!-- Basic -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"640\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">I_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Basic / Interface</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Reusable data foundation</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AccessControl.*, @EndUserText.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Composite views</text>\n\n  <!-- Private -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"680\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\"/>\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"680\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">P_* / none</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Private</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Internal logic, hidden from consumers</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">No UI annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Basic / Composite views</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>"},{"title":"CDS Source Code","language":"abap","codeBlock":"@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_VDMBAS'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - VDM Basic (Interface) View Type'\n@VDM.viewType: #BASIC\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION\n@ObjectModel.dataType: #BASIC\n@OData.publish: true\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC\n  as select from ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n{\n  key TravelId,\n      AgencyId,\n      CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      TotalPrice,\n      CurrencyCode,\n      Description,\n      Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Lastchangedat\n}"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC-concept-diagram\">Concept Diagram</h2>\n<div class=\"docs-diagram\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 1000 750\" font-family=\"'Ubuntu', sans-serif\">\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"arr\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n    </marker>\n    <marker id=\"arr-b\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z\" fill=\"#3B82F6\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n\n  <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"1000\" height=\"55\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"35\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"20\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">VDM (Virtual Data Model) Layer Architecture</text>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 4: Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"75\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\" stroke=\"#22C55E\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"98\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">Consumption View (Layer 4)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"115\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">C_* or R_* prefix · Fiori UI / OData · @UI.* / @Search / @Consumption.* annotations</text>\n\n  <!-- Arrow -->\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"125\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"150\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n  <text x=\"520\" y=\"142\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#64748B\">consumes</text>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 3: Composite -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"155\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\" stroke=\"#EAB308\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"178\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">Composite View (Layer 3)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"195\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">C_* prefix · Joins multiple Basic views · Business logic, aggregations, currency conversion</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"210\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: C_Travel_Agency — joins Travel + Agency + Booking</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"220\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"245\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 2: Basic / Interface -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"250\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\" stroke=\"#EF4444\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"273\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">Basic / Interface View (Layer 2)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"290\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">I_* prefix · Reusable data foundation · Field selection, aliases, simple filters</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"305\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: I_Travel / I_Booking — clean projection of DDIC tables</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"315\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"340\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- LAYER 1: Private -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"345\" width=\"900\" height=\"65\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\" stroke=\"#A855F7\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"368\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">Private View (Layer 1)</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"385\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">P_* prefix or no prefix · Internal abstraction · Complex joins, data enrichment, no UI annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"75\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#64748B\">Example: P_Travel_Aggregate — aggregation logic hidden from consumers</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"500\" y1=\"410\" x2=\"500\" y2=\"435\" stroke=\"#E95420\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#arr)\"/>\n\n  <!-- DB Source -->\n  <rect x=\"300\" y=\"440\" width=\"400\" height=\"40\" rx=\"6\" fill=\"#1E293B\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"463\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">HANA DB / DDIC Tables</text>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"476\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"#94A3B8\">/DMO/I_Travel_D / /DMO/I_Booking_D / /DMO/I_Agency / ...</text>\n\n  <!-- Right side: Naming conventions table -->\n  <rect x=\"50\" y=\"500\" width=\"900\" height=\"235\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#F8FAFC\" stroke=\"#CBD5E1\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n  <text x=\"500\" y=\"523\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1e293b\">VDM Naming Convention & Layer Purpose</text>\n  <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"530\" x2=\"930\" y2=\"530\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <!-- Table header -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"538\" width=\"860\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#E95420\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Prefix</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Layer</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Purpose</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"553\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#FFF\">Consumed By</text>\n\n  <line x1=\"70\" y1=\"560\" x2=\"930\" y2=\"560\" stroke=\"#E2E8F0\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n\n  <!-- Consumption -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"560\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#F0FDF4\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#16A34A\">C_* / R_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Consumption</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fiori UI, OData exposure</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@UI.*, @Search, @Consumption.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"580\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Fiori App / External API</text>\n\n  <!-- Composite -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"600\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#FEFCE8\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#CA8A04\">C_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Composite</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Business logic, joins, aggregations</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@ObjectModel.*, @Analytics.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Consumption views</text>\n\n  <!-- Basic -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"640\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#FEF2F2\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#DC2626\">I_*</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Basic / Interface</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Reusable data foundation</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">@AccessControl.*, @EndUserText.*</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"660\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Composite views</text>\n\n  <!-- Private -->\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"680\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\"/>\n  <rect x=\"70\" y=\"680\" width=\"860\" height=\"40\" rx=\"0\" fill=\"#EDE9FE\"/>\n  <text x=\"120\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#9333EA\">P_* / none</text>\n  <text x=\"250\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Private</text>\n  <text x=\"400\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Internal logic, hidden from consumers</text>\n  <text x=\"600\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">No UI annotations</text>\n  <text x=\"800\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#1e293b\">Basic / Composite views</text>\n<text x=\"10\" y=\"20\" font-size=\"8\" fill=\"rgba(233,84,32,0.15)\" font-family=\"sans-serif\">cds-bytes (c) 2026</text></svg></div>\n<h2 id=\"section-ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC-cds-source-code\">CDS Source Code</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-abap\">@AbapCatalog.sqlViewName: 'ZPRAC_SQL_VDMBAS'\n@AbapCatalog.compiler.compareFilter: true\n@AbapCatalog.preserveKey: true\n@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #CHECK\n@EndUserText.label: 'Practice CDS - VDM Basic (Interface) View Type'\n@VDM.viewType: #BASIC\n@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION\n@ObjectModel.dataType: #BASIC\n@OData.publish: true\ndefine view ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC\n  as select from ZPRAC_CDS_SIMPLE\n{\n  key TravelId,\n      AgencyId,\n      CustomerId,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      BeginDate,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      EndDate,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      BookingFee,\n      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'CurrencyCode'\n      TotalPrice,\n      CurrencyCode,\n      Description,\n      Status,\n      @Semantics.user.createdBy: true\n      Createdby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Createdat,\n      @Semantics.user.lastChangedBy: true\n      Lastchangedby,\n      @Semantics.date: true\n      Lastchangedat\n}</code></pre>","tags":["cds-view","vdm"],"details":"<p class=\"mb-2\">WHAT IS VDM?</p><p class=\"mb-2\">SAP's Virtual Data Model standardizes CDS view development into</p><p class=\"mb-2\">layered view types. Following VDM ensures:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">✓ Consistent naming and structure across the organization</p><p class=\"mb-2\">✓ Clear separation of concerns between layers</p><p class=\"mb-2\">✓ Easier maintenance and onboarding of new developers</p><p class=\"mb-2\">✓ Reusable building blocks for Fiori, Analytics, and OData</p><p class=\"mb-2\">VDM VIEW TYPES:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">┌──────────────┬──────────┬────────────────────────────────┐</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ Type         │ Notation │ Purpose                        │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">├──────────────┼──────────┼────────────────────────────────┤</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ #BASIC       │ I_*      │ Interface - direct table access│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ #COMPOSITE   │ C_*      │ Business logic / calculations  │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ #CONSUMPTION │ C_*      │ Final layer for consumers      │</p><p class=\"mb-2\">│ #PRIVATE     │ P_*      │ Internal helpers (not consumed)│</p><p class=\"mb-2\">└──────────────┴──────────┴────────────────────────────────┘</p><p class=\"mb-2\">BASIC VIEW CHARACTERISTICS:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">- Directly built on database tables or other #BASIC views</p><p class=\"mb-2\">- No/minimal business logic — pure data projection</p><p class=\"mb-2\">- Full field semantics (@Semantics.amount, @Semantics.date, etc.)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">- Named with I_ prefix in SAP standard: e.g. I_Travel_D</p><p class=\"mb-2\">- Foundation for all downstream composite/consumption views</p><p class=\"mb-2\">THIS EXAMPLE:</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@VDM.viewType: #BASIC  → Marks this as an Interface/Basic view</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@Analytics.dataCategory: #DIMENSION  → Used as a dimension in analytics</p><p class=\"mb-2\">@ObjectModel.dataType: #BASIC        → Core data type</p><p class=\"mb-2\">All fields have full @Semantics annotations (VDM requirement)</p><p class=\"mb-2\">DIAGRAM: assets/diagrams/vdm-layers.svg</p>","cdsViewName":"ZPRAC_CDS_VDM_BASIC","sqlViewName":"ZPRAC_SQL_VDMBAS","topic":"SAP Virtual Data Model — View Type: #BASIC"}